awemeId.description: The user's Douyin account can be viewed on the Douyin App user's personal homepage
awemeId.description_zh: 用户的抖音号，可以进入抖音 App 用户个人主页查看

type.description: Type, you can choose an avatar or a nickname
type.description_zh: 类型，可以选择头像或昵称

disableDefault.description: Disable the default behavior. When clicking on the profile picture, if the user is in the live broadcast state, they will jump to the live broadcast room by default, and if they are not in the live broadcast state, they will jump to the personal homepage. If true, there will be no default behavior when clicking on the avatar.
disableDefault.description_zh: 禁用默认行为。点击头像时，如果用户处于直播状态下默认会跳转到直播间，非直播状态下跳转到个人主页。如果为 true，点击头像时不会有默认行为。

defaultAvatar.description: The default avatar URL that appears when fetching information fails
defaultAvatar.description_zh: 获取信息失败时显示的默认头像 url

defaultText.description: The default nickname text that is displayed when fetching information fails
defaultText.description_zh: 获取信息失败时显示的默认昵称文本
